Title: Wilo Stratos MAXO-D 65/05-16 R7
Description: The Wilo Stratos Maxo-D R7 is an easy-to-use smart pump with one touch commissioning, EC motor, electronic power adjustment and permanent, automatic performance adaptation for optimum energy efficiency. The R7 version does not include an internal temperature sensor.  This twin head smart-pump has a range of functions for reliable use including heating and cooling quantity measurement, dry running detection and automatic No-Flow Stop, which deactivates the pump when no flow is detected.  Each pump operates individually with one main pump and one pump on standby, meaning if any faults are detected the pumps will automatically switch over to prevent failure.  This is an inline glandless pump, suitable to be used in domestic or light commercial buildings for all central heating, cooling, underfloor heating, water/glycol mixtures and air conditioning systems
